HEADWORD: anesthetist
<hw>anesthetist</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>A medical
specialist who administers an anesthetic to a patient before the patient
is treated.</def> <altsp>[Also spelled
<asp>anaesthetist</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> anesthesiologist.</syn>⟦br⟧
